title._content: Swedish navy in moonlight before a battle in July 1789, Öland, Sweden

description._content: The Swedish navy in line of battle, viewed by night in moonlight. The image is part of a series illustrating a naval battle at the southern point of the island of Öland in the Baltic Sea, fought in July 1789 in the war of 1788-1790 between Sweden and Russia. Watercoloured contour etching by Johan Petter Cumelin, from c. 1790. Svenska flottan i linjeformation, sedd om natten i månsken. Bilden hör till en serie som illustrerar ett sjöslag vid Ölands södra udde, utkämpat i juli 1789 under kriget mellan Sverige och Ryssland 1788-1790. Akvarellerad konturetsning av Johan Petter Cumelin, från cirka 1790. Collection: The Rosenhane Collection, Library of Swedish National Heritage Board (Vitterhetsakademiens bibliotek ) Parish (socken): Ås Province (landskap): Öland Municipality (kommun): Mörbylånga County (län): Kalmar Photograph by: Jan Eve Olsson Date: 1995 Persistent URL: kmb.raa.se/cocoon/bild/show-image.html?id=16001000020524 Read more about the photo database (in english): www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/about.html
